snippet.title: Change: A Homeless Survival Experience - Early access announcement trailer
snippet.description:
We are proud to announce that our passion project, CHANGE, is coming to Steam early access on the 18th of September 2018! 

20% of profits will be going to charities focused on the issue of homelessness. 

www.delveinteractive.com
